api = idb.IDAPython(kernel32_idb)
assert api.ida_entry.get_entry_qty() == 1572
assert api.ida_entry.get_entry_ordinal(0) == 1
assert api.ida_entry.get_entry(api.ida_entry.get_entry_ordinal(0)
    ) == 1754273581
assert api.ida_entry.get_entry_name(api.ida_entry.get_entry_ordinal(0)
    ) == 'BaseThreadInitThunk'
assert api.ida_entry.get_entry_forwarder(api.ida_entry.get_entry_ordinal(16)
    ) is None
assert api.ida_entry.get_entry_ordinal(1572) == 1754273429
assert api.ida_entry.get_entry_name(1754273429) == 'DllEntryPoint'
kern32_test()
